name: total-auto-cargo-miss-upper
title: Total Auto Cargo Missed (Upper)
description: Total number of cargo that missed the upper hub (and did not score in lower hub) during Auto
function:
let failed = data.eventLog.filter((event) => (event.name === 'fail_port' && event.variables.hub === 'upper' && event.timeStamp <= 15));
return failed.length;
